SELECT
    book_ref,
    book_date,
    total_amount,
    ticket_no,
    passenger_id,
    passenger_name,
    flight_id,
    flight_no,
    scheduled_departure,
    scheduled_arrival,
    actual_departure,
    actual_arrival,
    departure_airport,
    departure_airport_name,
    departure_city,
    departure_timezone,
    arrival_airport,
    arrival_airport_name,
    arrival_city,
    arrival_timezone,
    fare_conditions,
    amount
FROM
(
    SELECT
        b.book_ref,
        b.book_date,
        b.total_amount,
        t.ticket_no,
        t.passenger_id,
        t.passenger_name,
        f.flight_id,
        f.flight_no,
        f.scheduled_departure,
        f.scheduled_arrival,
        f.actual_departure,
        f.actual_arrival,
        f.departure_airport,
        f.arrival_airport,
        a1.airport_name AS departure_airport_name,
        a1.city AS departure_city,
        a1.timezone AS departure_timezone,
        a2.airport_name AS arrival_airport_name,
        a2.city AS arrival_city,
        a2.timezone AS arrival_timezone,
        tf.fare_conditions,
        tf.amount
    FROM
        bookings b
        JOIN tickets t ON b.book_ref = t.book_ref
        JOIN ticket_flights tf ON t.ticket_no = tf.ticket_no
        JOIN flights f ON tf.flight_id = f.flight_id
        JOIN airports_data a1 ON f.departure_airport = a1.airport_code
        JOIN airports_data a2 ON f.arrival_airport = a2.airport_code
)
ORDER BY
    book_date DESC,
    scheduled_departure ASC
